<p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p>Your account has been locked due to an excessive number of unsuccessful sign in attempts.</p>
<p>由于尝试登录失败的次数过多，您的帐户已被锁定。</p>

<br />

<p>Even if the correct username and password are entered after the account is locked, the login will not be successful, thus preventing brute force cracking of the username/password from the Internet.</p>
<p>账号锁定后即使输入正确的用户名和密码也不会登录成功，从而可以防止来自互联网上的用户名/密码的暴力破解。</p>

<br />


<p>Click the link below to unlock your account:</p>
<p>点击下面的链接以解锁您的帐户：</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Unlock my account', unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token) %></p>
